✅ Phase 10C: Hybrid Retrieval (Vector + BM25)
What you’re building in this phase

Instead of ranking chunks only by vector similarity, you’ll compute:

Vector score (semantic meaning)

BM25 score (keyword relevance)

Hybrid score = weighted combination

This fixes broad queries like “what does X need to work” where keywords matter.

